 * **Enumerations:**
 * - `data_enum` - Type system (primitives, vectors, nested vectors)
 * - `opt_enum` - Optimizer types (adam, sgd, rmsprop, etc.)
 * - `loss_enum` - Loss functions (bce, mse, cross_entropy, etc.)
 * - `mode_enum` - Training modes (training, validation, evaluation)
 * - `graph_enum` - Graph data types (data/truth/pred for graph/node/edge)
 * - `particle_enum` - Particle properties (pt, eta, phi, energy, etc.)
 * - `scheduler_enum` - Learning rate schedulers
